        <hr><img src="ccs.jpeg" width="51%"><hr>
        <details>
            <summary>Read More</summary>
            <p>Cybersecurity is the practice of protecting systems, networks, and programs from digital attacks. <br>These cyberattacks are usually aimed at accessing, changing, or destroying sensitive information;<br> extorting money from users via ransomware; or interrupting normal business processes.</p>
            </details>
        <li style="background-color:blue;">Data analytics</li>
